### Authenicate

POST http://localhost:4242/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "super-secret"
}

> {% client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken); %}

### Add a new employee

POST http://localhost:4242/api/v1/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Per Andersson"
}